text: Alatorka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kaltymanovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 718 as of 2010. There are 21 streets. == Geography == It is located 11 km from Iglino, 8 km from Kaltymanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Alatorka
